    "description": "Will the Pandas get you?<br />\r\nThe Back Rooms have haunted a generation. No one knows how they get there; no one knows how to get out. Evil could lurk beyond any corner in this labyrinth. It’s your worst nightmare come true, you hear them scratching at the walls, the footsteps echoing, but getting closer. There are signs on the walls, prayers for help. But others are written in human blood. It’s the Pandas and they’re taunting you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n•\tA psychological horror game set in the Back Rooms<br />\r\n•\tRun and hide as giant pandas chase you from level to level. Each with its own unique ability to make your life hell.<br />\r\n•\tEach level increases in difficulty.<br />\r\n•\tMake your way to safe rooms where the nightmarish pandas can’t get you… you hope.<br />\r\n•\tCollect power-ups to fight off the pandas, but it won’t last long.<br />\r\n•\tSingle player, first person.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCan you make your way through the Back Rooms with your Mind and Body intact? <br />\r\nOr will the Pandas drag you deeper?",
